            <div class="tn-app-hero__text">
                <h1 class="tn-agency-hero__text text-white lh-base"><strong>
                        Everything Your Clients Need <br><span class="highlight highlight--agency"
                                                               style="background-image: url(/images/tn-agency-bundles-highlight.svg); padding: 0px 18px;">to Build Trust and Credibility</span>
                    </strong></h1>
                <h2 class="text-white pe-lg-5 pe-sm-0 pe-0 fs-3"><strong>Email Signature Widget | QR Code App | Social
                        Media Automation</strong></h2>
                <p class="apps-text text-white fw-bold">TrustNinja provides a complete 3-in-1 Review Management
                    Software that helps businesses generate more reviews, monitor feedback, and promote positive
                    customer experiences.

                    <br><br>All features are available within your white-label environment.</p>
                <div class="tn-agency-hero__cta-buttons mt-4">
