                <h4 class="text-white fw-bold"><span class="red-highlight-sub-heading">QR Code Review App</span></h4>
                <h2 class="qr-main-section-heading my-3">Instant Reviews at the Point of Service</h2>
                <div class="d-flex my-3">
                    <div class="me-3">
